summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City of Seattle Comprehensive Plan and the South Park potential annexation area, authorizing the Mayor to execute a Memorandum of Understanding that establishes a process and schedule for negotiation and resolution with the City of Tukwila and King County of issues relating to the potential annexation area and other unincorporated area and boundary issues, including responsibility for the 16th Avenue South bridge.
note: No text was filed for this legislation. Instead, Resolution 29594 was substituted in lieu of 111764.
